Aspect	MatchToken	Comparator
Purpose	Prepare data	Compare data
Stage	Before comparison	During comparison
Input	Raw attribute value	Tokenized values
Output	Tokens	Similarity score
Focus	Normalization	Accuracy
Examples	LOWERCASE, PHONETIC, NGRAM	EXACT, FUZZY, JARO
-----
In Reltio, MatchToken prepares and standardizes attribute values for matching, while Comparator evaluates similarity between those prepared values to calculate a match score....
